CLAUDE.md
help_tab_text.txt

# Sibling Rust project with its own git repo — the Deeps port reads from
# it for source-of-truth parity but the source isn't part of KazBars's
# release surface. Regenerate the parity fixture via Deeps/rust/parity-dump/.
# Root-anchored (leading /) so case-insensitive Windows git doesn't also
# ignore the bundled `src/kazbars/assets/deeps/` registry.
/Deeps/
